      • addTwistWrenchTrafo

        public void addTwistWrenchTrafo(com.kuka.geometry.Frame measureFrame,
                                com.kuka.geometry.Frame orientationFrame)
        Adds the TwistWrenchTrafo module to the SPR. The port IDs as reported by #getForcePortID() and #getVariancePortID() will be changed accordingly.

        The transformation fed in to the module will be computed such that:

        • the translation will be the static translation from the robot flange to the origin of measureFrame;
        • the rotation will be the (possibly dynamic) rotation that rotates from the robot flange orientation to the orientation of orientationFrame.
        Parameters:
        measureFrame - the measure frame
        orientationFrame - the orientation frame; may be identical to measureFrame
